Headline: "TransUnion analyzed results for US Bank's HELOC September 2025 Prescreen mail campaign"
Points:

Campaign based on a mail file of 74,381 consumers and a control file of 8,068 consumers, both provided directly by US Bank

Full Control group of 8,068
Filtered Control group of 8,035


Mailing based on homeowner equity and tenure criteria, segmented into three tiers:

HI60: open mortgage, lendable equity ≥ $60,000, tenure ≥ 10 years
HI40: open mortgage, lendable equity ≥ $40,000, tenure of 3–5 years
GEN: open mortgage, general use (doesn't meet the HI60/HI40 equity and tenure thresholds)


74,381 consumers selected for mailing, all with open mortgages
Performance window of Oct 5, 2025 – Feb 18, 2026 — Campaign Window (Oct 5, 2025 – Nov 20, 2025) plus buffer time to ensure enough time is provided for account opening



